---
import LayoutCommon from '../layouts/layout-common.astro'
---

<LayoutCommon>
	<div id="about" class="things-block">
		<h1>关于这个博客🎳</h1>
		<p>我想许多人搭建博客的初衷都是构建一个网络日志，还能学到许多前端知识，何乐而不为？</p>
		<p>无独有偶，站点基于 <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank">Astro.js</a> 搭建，几乎没有外部库，保证了极致的
			<b>精简快速</b></p>
		<p style="margin-top: 20px"><b>Technology involved:</b><span>Astro.js</span><span>TailwindCSS</span><a
			href="https://github.com/Nesb01t/meteor-template" target="_blank"><span>SourceCode @Github</span></a>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div id="frontend" class="things-block">
		<h1>WEB 前端</h1>
	</div>
	<div id="gameplay" class="things-block">
		<h1>Gameplay 开发</h1>
	</div>
</LayoutCommon>

<style>
  .things-block {
    height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 5rem;
    border-top: rgba(54, 49, 38, 0.3) 2px dashed;;
    background-color: rgb(246, 226, 228);
  }

  .things-block h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .things-block p {
    position: relative;

    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 80vw;
    margin-left: 10vw;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .things-block a {
    color: steelblue;
  }

  .things-block span {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background-color: rgba(143, 151, 114, 0.3);
  }

  .things-block a span {
    color: whitesmoke;
    background-color: black;
  }

	.things-block a span:hover {
		color: steelblue;
	}
</style>